I made this recipe with boneless skinless chicken thighs, and it was luscious. My boyfriend adored it! I don't know if it contributed to its deliciousness, but I made it several days in advance of when we ended up eating it. It warmed up beautifully and was delicious served over couscous. I chopped the green herbs and left them in, and I skipped the almonds. I will definitely be making this all through the fall and winter!

